  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Enjoy breakfast out on the panoramic terrace, whilst enjoying the beautiful views down towards Ravello and along the coast. Breakfast includes things like a fresh pastries, fruit and yogurt. </p>
<p><strong>Gli Ulivi Restaurant </strong>has a beautiful seating area where you can dine overlooking Ravello and the Amalfi Coast. The restaurant has a wide selection of dishes including plenty of fresh seafood and local ingredients, some of which is produced on the terraces that surround the Villa, from the vineyards and olive groves to the vegetable and herb garden. It's renowned for its great service and has an extensive wine store. </p>
<p><strong>Lounge Bar Pascal</strong> serves original cocktails and has a good wine list.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
