  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>We love this small and intimate hotel on the Amalfi Coast. It's in a quiet setting in the hills above Ravello - the sea views from up here are amazing. There's a nice pool area and traditionally-styled rooms with pieces of ceramic from the owner's local business. There's only seven rooms here so you'll feel very comfortable and well taken care of. </p>]]></listingDescription>
