  <locationDescription><![CDATA[<p><span><strong>Bus</strong></span></p>
<p><span>There is a bus stop about 500 metres from the Villa that departs towards Amalfi once every hour. </span></p>
<p><span>The bus stop slightly closer, about 30 metres from the Villa that departs towards Amalfi three times per day. </span></p>
<p><span>From Amalfi you'll find buses &amp; boats to Positano, Capri, Sorrento, Salerno and Naples.</span></p>]]></locationDescription>
