  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p>You can relax in pure luxury at Palazzo Pacal - every room has a memory foam mattress with Frette Italian linen and down duvets. The little details like the bathrobes and designer toiletries are the thoughtful touches that make this hotel the perfect place to relax after days spent exploring the Amalfi Coast.</p>
<p><strong>Iris - Superior Room</strong> is about 25m² and has a small French balcony and sea views. It sleeps two people in a double or two single beds and is located on the ground floor. All of the rooms are thoughtfully decorated with handmade ceramics, mirrors, luxurious fabrics and beautiful patterned tiled floors. They all have a shower, TV, tea &amp; coffee maker, minibar, bath robes, air conditioning, safe, laptop work-space and iron/ironing board (on request). This room is available on request, please call to book. Baby cots are available on request, free of charge.</p>
<p><strong>Edera - Deluxe Room </strong>is about 25m² and has a private furnished terrace with a sea view. This room sleeps two people and is available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Ortensia - Junior Suite</strong> is about 40m² and haw sea views through six portal windows. Its located on the top floor and can sleep 2- 4 people in two singles or a double bed, the extra bed is a sofa bed. This room is available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Rosa - Canina Grand Deluxe</strong> <strong>Suite </strong>is about 40m² and has a French balcony with sea views. Its located on the ground floor of the villa. This room has a kitchen area with a hob, oven, microwave, cooking utensils and dishes. It can sleep 2- 3 people in two singles or a double bed, the extra bed is a sofa bed. This room is available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>Ibisco - Executive Suite </strong>is an apartment that’s about 50m² and has a private furnished terrace with amazing sea views over the Amalfi Coast. This room is located on the ground floor of the villa and has a separate kitchen with a full-sized fridge-freezer, hob, oven and microwave. It has a small living area and sleeps 2- 4 people in two singles or a double bed, the extra bed is a sofa bed.</p>
<p><strong>Lillà - Executive Romantic Suite </strong>is about 30m², has a French balcony and a private terrace with one of the best sea views in the property. Its located on the first floor and sleeps 2- 3 people in two singles or a double bed, the extra bed is a sofa bed.</p>
<p><strong>Fiordaliso - Prestige Suite</strong> is about 40m², has a large private terrace with sun loungers, table and chairs and sea views. Its sleeps 2- 4 people in two singles or a double bed, the extra bed is a sofa bed. The suite has a separate living room and is available on request, please call to book.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
